aa(lp75
VThe best way to explain this to you is by showing you two cases.
p76
aVThe first is the case  of the military diary.
p77
aVNow this is a document that was smuggled out of somewhere in 1999.
p78
aVAnd what you see there is the state following individuals,
p79
aVpeople that, like you,  wanted to change their country,
p80
aVand they jotted everything down.
p81
aVAnd one of the things that they wrote  down is when they executed them.
p82
aVInside that yellow rectangle,  you see a code,
p83
aVit's a secret code: 300.
p84
aVAnd then you see a date.
p85
aVThe 300 means "executed" and the date  means when they were executed.
p86
aVNow that's going to come into play in a second.
