VBut most important is about two weeks later,
p100
aVwe go another hit, another match
p101
aVfrom the same grave to Amancio Villatoro.
p102
aVThe DNA of that body also matched the DNA of that family.
p103
aVAnd then we noticed that he was also in the diary.
p104
aVBut it was amazing to see that he was  also executed on March 29, 1984.
p105
aVSo that led us to think, hmm,  how many bodies were in the grave?
p106
aVSix.
p107
aVSo then we said, how many people were executed on March 29, 1984?
p108
aVThat's right, six as well.
p109
aVSo we have Juan de Dios, Hugo, Moises and Zoilo.
