aVGrave 15, what we noticed, was a grave full of women and children,
p138
aV63 of them.
p139
aVAnd that immediately made us think,
p140
aVmy goodness, where is there a case like this?
p141
aVWhen I got to Guatemala in 1995,
p142
aVI heard of a case of a massacre that happened on May 14, 1982,
p143
aVwhere the army came in, killed the men,
p144
aVand took the women and children  in helicopters to an unknown location.
